name: Detail Collection Report
query:
select
 owner_name as 'Owner:Owner:200',house as 'House',collection as 'Collection:Collection:130', amount as 'Amount',
 paid_amount as 'Paid',remaining_amount as 'Remaining:Remaining:110',dues as 'Dues',deposit as 'Deposit',month as 'Month'
from `tabcollectioninfo`
